OL,7,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,8,Fat six hospitals in the West Midlands
OL,9,Fincluding in Birmingham, Solihull,
OL,10,FStafford and Stoke-on-Trent.
OL,12,FUniversity Hospitals Birmingham NHS
OL,13,FFoundation Trust, which runs Good
OL,14,FHope, Heartlands and Queen Elizabeth
OL,15,Fhospitals in Birmingham as well as
OL,16,FSolihull Hospital said it was due to
OL,17,F"exceptional" numbers of patients with
OL,18,Fflu.
