OL,5,Chospitals
OL,7,FA spokesperson said 269 patients with
OL,8,Fflu required hospital admission - with
OL,9,Fmask-wearing being introduced across
OL,10,Fall clinical departments.
OL,12,FCurrently the number of people in
OL,13,Fhospital with flu in England is at a
OL,14,Frecord level for this time of year.
OL,16,FThe hospital trust has said their
OL,17,Femergency departments remain
OL,18,F"overcrowded with extended waits to be
OL,19,Fseen."
