OL,7,FIn a statement, the trust said:
OL,8,F"Despite expanding capacity in our
OL,9,Fwards and in our emergency
OL,10,Fdepartments, our emergency departments
OL,11,F(A&Es) remain overcrowded with
OL,12,Fextended waits to be seen.
OL,14,F"We are asking the communities we
OL,15,Fserve to think carefully about how
OL,16,Fthey access healthcare - if you do not
OL,17,Fhave an emergency or life-threatening
OL,18,Fcondition you may be redirected to
OL,19,Fanother healthcare service such as a
OL,20,Fpharmacy or NHS 111."
