OL,7,FIt comes just hours after the
OL,8,FUniversity Hospitals of North Midlands
OL,9,Fsaid it was currently experiencing
OL,10,Fextremely high demand with both Royal
OL,11,FStoke University Hospital and County
OL,12,FHospital, Stafford, having been under
OL,13,Fsevere and sustained pressure for the
OL,14,Flast week.
OL,16,FPatients were being warned of long
OL,17,Fdelays and are urged to only visit A&E
OL,18,Fin a life-threatening emergency.
OL,20,FRecord flu levels create added strain
OL,21,Fon hospitals
