OL,5,Chospitals
OL,7,FAn average of 1,717 flu patients were
OL,8,Fin beds in England each day, including
OL,9,F69 in critical care, the most recent
OL,10,Fdata showed.
OL,12,FThis is 56% higher than the equivalent
OL,13,Fnumbers for the same week in 2024,
OL,14,Fwhen the total was 1,098 with 39 in
OL,15,Fcritical care.
OL,17,FIt is also well above levels seen in
OL,18,Fboth 2023 (243 patients) and 2022
OL,19,F(772).
