OL,7,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,8,Fhas called on people to get a flu jab.
OL,10,FUKHSA data suggests this year's
OL,11,Fvaccine is providing good protection
OL,12,Feven though a drifted influenza
OL,13,FA(H3N2) strain ` dubbed super flu ` is
OL,14,Fcurrently dominating cases in England.
OL,16,FPatients at the University Hospitals
OL,17,Fof North Midlands were being warned of
OL,18,Flong delays and are urged to only
OL,19,Fvisit A&E in a life-threatening
OL,20,Femergency.
