OL,7,FKaty Thorpe, UHNM Chief Operating
OL,8,FOfficer said: "We have taken the
OL,9,Fdifficult decision to declare a
OL,10,Fcritical incident.
OL,12,F"This helps us to take additional
OL,13,Fmeasures to maintain safe services for
OL,14,Four patients and those in the
OL,15,Fcommunity waiting for an ambulance.
